      <li><a href="#leadership" class="hover:text-navy transition-colors">Leadership and Management of the Curriculum</a></li>
      <li><a href="#delivery" class="hover:text-navy transition-colors">Delivery of the Curriculum</a></li>
      <li><a href="#teaching-and-learning" class="hover:text-navy transition-colors">Teaching and Learning</a></li>
      <li><a href="#breakdown" class="hover:text-navy transition-colors">Breakdown of Curriculum</a></li>
